{"tid":1746931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［經典重溫］鄭松泰秘密錄音流出　稱「公眾係白痴」：以為我哋係本土派","createTime":"2019-11-23T03:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T04:26:07.000Z","uid":4599,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1418e24b8de74e3a6a25b6c2af98b9ba7cedcf","tid":1746931,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:43:45.000Z","msg":"「熱普城」去年在立法會選舉失利，僅熱血公民鄭松泰贏得議席，「教主」黃毓民爆冷敗於青年新政游蕙禎，早前更宣布退出政壇，但「熱普城」內鬥風波近日愈演愈烈。<br />\n<br />\n知名網民「無敵神駒」昨晚（10日）在網上直播節目，播出一段聲稱是鄭松泰於熱血公民內部會議的「絕密錄音」，當中鄭松泰爆粗怒罵梁游「應該去死」，但自己要在公眾面前「同佢哋扮friend」，「顯示畀人睇我係幫緊佢哋」，更稱「公眾係白痴，以為我哋係本土派」，事件引起網上極大爭議。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰在Facebook證實錄音屬實，稱對「手足沒有遵守黨規和破壞內部溝通指引」，深表遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎啦熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f6807349ede6e00a7db97e631fa2e6fe8b192eb0","tid":1746931,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"咬我啊熱狗！"},{"pid":"b449070c70f973a7a418c886a0c986b4c30f8303","tid":1746931,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"狠狠地咬我！"},{"pid":"aaabfb0ab927ef2eb03bfc7861897dc6d228bb0e","tid":1746931,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:48:52.000Z","msg":"好慘啊滿仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92dbdae6326adaa30ae4d58381980603196d3b90","tid":1746931,"uid":43717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd8ec6f4406447b7cfd7260bb43b16dcfac3891","tid":1746931,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a02b77e6f3161248642ef6f34111ce354ff7df1","tid":1746931,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:01:56.